title: Tool - Lateralus [16-bit 44.1kHz HDCD flac] MC Lurken Mix
description:
Tool - Lateralus [24-bit 96kHz HDCD flac] MC Lurken Mix



**MC Lurken Mix featuring custom Izotope Ozone 5 VST (EQ, Dynamics, Imaging, Dither) and 64-bit/384kHz processing. Presented in CD quality 16-bit/44.1kHz**



A couple months ago I ran across this vinyl rip of Lateralus (http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/8261839/TOOL_Lateralus_%28LINN_LP12_vinyl%29_FLAC) posted on a vinyl rip site. In a topic of this rip there was a claim that this was the best version out there. My remaster of Lateralus (http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/8086539/Tool_-_Lateralus_-_Custom_Remaster_by_MC_Lurken_16-bit_44.1kHz_f) was also brought into the conversation with some people claiming they liked mine better. Knowing I could do better after some recent improvements I have decided to do another version. Lateralus is quickly becoming one of my favorite albums and I hope you all enjoy this new version as much as I do.
